dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4multiplatform

Interface IGateway

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IGateway
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IGateway: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A gateway is an ECU that is connected to two or more clusters (channels, but not redundant), and performs a frame, Pdu or signal mapping between them.
